Maintainer: Brent Baccala <cosine@freesoft.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), nodejs, npm

Package: bbb-plugin-remote-desktop
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: BigBlueButton remote desktop plugin
 Adds VNC remote desktop sharing to BigBlueButton v3.0 via the plugin
 architecture. Moderators can share a VNC desktop in the presentation
 area. No core BBB modifications required.
